      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in incredible shape\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, you won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It drives like a total dream and has been pampered since day one. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see this beauty in person!",
