    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'showroom condition.' This single-owner masterpiece has been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed weekly. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating, with absolutely zero stone chips, dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine, factory-fresh state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear, and the interior retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. Every feature, from the advanced driver-assist systems to the panoramic sunroof, functions perfectly. With ultra-low mileage and a rigorous history of preventative maintenance, this car offers a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands a vehicle indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 46500.0,
